==Documentation==
This template creates a full person page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

People are real individuals involved in the video game industry - developers, designers, voice actors,
composers, journalists, and other notable figures.

